Package: ishpR
Type: Package
Title: Iterative search for hyper-parameters in penalized regression models
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2019-05-20
Author: Juan C. Laria, M. Carmen Aguilera Morillo, Rosa E. Lillo
Maintainer: Juan C. Laria <juancarlos.laria@uc3m.es>
Description: Implements a standard solver for lasso, group-lasso and sparse group-lasso regularization in linear models, 
          with arbitrary loss functions (e.g. mean squared error, binary cross-entropy, cox proportional hazard models log-likelihood). 
          In addition, several hyper-parameter search methods are included. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.0)
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    gridExtra,
    dplyr,
    magrittr
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
